text: Sabine Lisicki (; born 22 September 1989 in Troisdorf) is a German professional tennis player. Lisicki won her first WTA title match in more than three seasons in Hong Kong in September 2014. She reached her high rank of world no. 12 on 21 May 2012 in singles. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:German tennis players Category:Sportspeople from North Rhine-Westphalia
